00:06:52.287 --> 00:06:54.122 position:50% align:center
[BOTH giggle]

00:07:01.463 --> 00:07:04.174 position:50% align:center
[ERIKA]
I never knew this was here!

00:07:04.257 --> 00:07:06.468 position:50% align:center
What a gorgeous place to meet!

00:07:10.347 --> 00:07:14.100 position:50% align:center
[ERIKA]
Oh, man, I'm a whole hour early.

00:07:14.184 --> 00:07:16.186 position:50% align:center
