00:09:04.669 --> 00:09:06.087 position:50% align:center
[laughs]

00:09:08.256 --> 00:09:11.217 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI] Thank you so much for
coming to spend the day with me!

00:09:11.301 --> 00:09:12.886 position:50% align:center
