00:10:37.387 --> 00:10:40.640 position:50% align:center
Minnow! Well,
that's a cool name!

00:10:40.724 --> 00:10:44.352 position:50% align:center
[ERIKA] She's amazing, catching
a fish with a thing like that.

00:10:46.771 --> 00:10:48.273 position:50% align:center
