00:14:39.170 --> 00:14:40.755 position:50% align:center
Look at it go.

00:14:43.174 --> 00:14:45.427 position:50% align:center
[BOTH] We're gonna
play in the water now!

00:15:08.116 --> 00:15:12.704 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI] Hey, Erika.
Did you have fun today?

00:15:21.254 --> 00:15:23.882 position:50% align:center
[ERIKA]
Yes. A lot!

00:15:28.595 --> 00:15:29.763 position:50% align:center
[KOMICHI]
Need fresh clothes?

00:15:29.846 --> 00:15:31.890 position:50% align:center
I have some.

00:15:31.973 --> 00:15:33.350 position:50% align:center
